hopobject.name: Page
hopobject.body: Thanks for calling medco-corp.com Given the company's current operational profile - somewhat limited scale and single geography presence - the ratings sit most comfortably at the 'BBB' level. While the financial profile compares well with the 'BBB' peer group, a higher rated single market operator would be expected to have a materially stronger (market number one or two) business position in turn resulting in a considerably stronger margin profile.
